# Mosquitto ACL for whz-lora.
#
# chirpstack — internal ChirpStack MQTT client: full access to application
# events and gateway topics.
user chirpstack
topic readwrite #

# testsubscriber — read-only subscriber for smoke testing and research consumers.
# Restrict to application uplink events; no write access.
user testsubscriber
topic read application/#
topic read eu868/gateway/#
